data.description: New 3-4 bdrm., 2 bath home on 8.8 beautiful acres full of wild life. Home has a LG kitchen on the main level w/SS appliances & an additional SM kitchen downstairs (no appliances included).   There is a bonus room that can be an office or a 4th bdrm.  The upper level has electric heaters in every room that are secondary to a new pellet stove with thermostat that heats the entire home.   A Lg. utility room has new washer/dryer on pedestals, 2 sheds, a pavilion with an OPTIONAL Hot Tub wired directly to an outside 200 amp panel box, a huge fire pit & lots of parking.   Home is 1 mile to amenities & Less than 5 mins to Lake George.   Come take a look and bring appropriate clothing and shoes to explore the beautiful 8.8 acres!
